- Right. He was Soo Mi.
- I remember that now.

242
00:08:01,023 --> 00:08:03,562
(This girl fired up the trainees when they were losing their focus.)

243
00:08:03,563 --> 00:08:04,563
(Shouting a word of encouragement)

244
00:08:04,564 --> 00:08:07,403
(With her excellent dancing skills and smooth stage presence...)

245
00:08:07,803 --> 00:08:10,203
(Lee Soo Mi placed 1st in "Girls on a Mission 101.")

246
00:08:10,803 --> 00:08:13,742
(She became the girl that most Koreans loved.)

247
00:08:13,743 --> 00:08:15,912
(1st place, 32 votes, SM Culture and Contents, Lee Soo Mi)

248
00:08:15,913 --> 00:08:18,342
- Soo Mi! I remember that now.
- I can't believe them.

249
00:08:18,343 --> 00:08:19,512
- How could you forget about that?
- I totally forgot.

250
00:08:19,513 --> 00:08:20,882
- Soo Mi.
- Soo Mi.

251
00:08:20,883 --> 00:08:23,052
- Soo Mi.
- Soo Geun was Lee Soo Mi.

252
00:08:23,053 --> 00:08:24,782
- We all dressed up as girls.
- How could they forget that?

253
00:08:24,783 --> 00:08:26,952
- That's right. I'm sorry.
- It was ten years ago.

254
00:08:26,953 --> 00:08:30,122
- You really hurt my feelings.
- Oh, that's right.

255
00:08:30,123 --> 00:08:32,292
- We had a team get-together too.
- He wore a mid-length wig.

256
00:08:32,293 --> 00:08:33,722
- It was ten years ago.
- Really?

257
00:08:33,723 --> 00:08:34,862
Don't you remember we had a team get-together?

258
00:08:34,863 --> 00:08:35,932
We didn't have a team get-together.

259
00:08:35,933 --> 00:08:37,033
- We didn't.
- What...

260
00:08:37,593 --> 00:08:39,502
- What was that?
- You remember that clearly.

261
00:08:39,503 --> 00:08:40,662
- You remember that, - There was no team get-together.

262
00:08:40,663 --> 00:08:42,032
