263
00:08:42,033 --> 00:08:43,302
- He's right.
- Hey.

264
00:08:43,303 --> 00:08:45,372
You remember that we didn't have a team get-together.

265
00:08:45,373 --> 00:08:47,802
- You must be upset.
- But you don't remember I won.

266
00:08:47,803 --> 00:08:49,142
- It's been too long.
- I'm upset.

267
00:08:49,143 --> 00:08:50,242
- It was ten years ago.
- Hey, I was going to...

268
00:08:50,243 --> 00:08:52,042
- Right.
- approve your enrollment,

269
00:08:52,043 --> 00:08:53,643
