387
00:13:01,823 --> 00:13:02,862
- Na Young, you're...
- Oh, come on!

388
00:13:02,863 --> 00:13:03,893
better with words than I expected.

389
00:13:04,333 --> 00:13:05,633
- We...
- I mean...

390
00:13:05,933 --> 00:13:07,432
I should do my best since I came here after a long time.

391
00:13:07,433 --> 00:13:10,002
- Shall I tell you what's funny?
- Yes, please tell us.

392
00:13:10,003 --> 00:13:12,072
You said Ho Dong learned about the guests by rote.

393
00:13:12,073 --> 00:13:13,872
- Yes.
- She read the script all day long.

394
00:13:13,873 --> 00:13:15,572
