395
00:13:15,573 --> 00:13:17,972
- That's right.
- She memorized her lines.

396
00:13:17,973 --> 00:13:19,542
- She practiced a lot.
- She always does her best.

397
00:13:19,543 --> 00:13:21,313
- Do everything you practiced.
- Right.

398
00:13:22,183 --> 00:13:23,852
- Next up is Chungha.
- What's Chungha's nickname?

399
00:13:23,853 --> 00:13:27,052
Her nickname is React-Chung.

400
00:13:27,053 --> 00:13:28,252
