468
00:15:50,433 --> 00:15:53,802
- Make me sweat, make me water - We know that song.

469
00:15:53,803 --> 00:15:55,632
So Hye used to be a little bit scared...

470
00:15:55,633 --> 00:15:57,432
- of dancing.
- I know.

471
00:15:57,433 --> 00:16:00,903
But she turned into a dancing queen while we prepared for our new album.

472
00:16:01,573 --> 00:16:03,013
Can you show us one more time?

473
00:16:03,313 --> 00:16:04,942
- I think we can laugh this time.
